message.body: Hey! Any interest in going to the Barnes foundation on tues 12/30? I'm sure you've been (I haven't!) but just thought I'd ask :)
I haven't been yet! And yes!
I think we need to buy timed tickets so we should touch base again a couple days before!
Yes, definitely. I'm so excited!! I've been wanting to go for awhile. I went to the old one a million times, but I've been too emotional to go to the new one. It is def time though
Aw. Yes, seize the day! I never went to the old one :/
